column2: <th aria-label="Player" class="poptip sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting left" data-stat="player" scope="col">Player</th>
column3: <th aria-label="Tm" class="poptip sort_default_asc show_partial_when_sorting left" data-stat="team" scope="col">Tm</th>
column4: <th aria-label="Age" class="poptip sort_default_asc center" data-stat="age" data-tip="Player's age on December 31st of that year" scope="col">Age</th>
column5: <th aria-label="Pos" class="poptip sort_default_asc left" data-stat="pos" data-tip="Position" scope="col">Pos</th>
column6: <th aria-label="Games" class="poptip center" data-stat="g" data-tip="Games played" scope="col">G</th>
column7: <th aria-label="Games Started" class="poptip center" data-stat="gs" data-tip="Games started as an offensive or defensive player" scope="col">GS</th>
column8: <th aria-label="QB Record" class="poptip center" data-stat="qb_rec" data-tip="Team record in games started by this QB (regular season)" scope="col">QBrec</th>
column9: <th aria-label="Passes Completed" class="poptip center" data-stat="pass_cmp" data-tip="Passes completed" scope="col">Cmp</th>
column10: <th aria-label="Pass Attempts" class="poptip center" data-stat="pass_att" data-tip="Passes attempted" scope="col">Att</th>
column11: <th aria-label="Pass Completion %" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Pass Completion %" data-stat="pass_cmp_perc" data-tip="Percentage of Passes Completed<br>Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." scope="col">Cmp%</th>
column12: <th aria-label="Passing Yds" class="poptip center" data-stat="pass_yds" data-tip="Yards Gained by Passing<br>For teams, sack yardage is deducted from this total" scope="col">Yds</th>

column14: <th aria-label="Passing TD %" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Passing TD %" data-stat="pass_td_perc" data-tip="Percentage of Touchdowns Thrown when Attempting to Pass <br>Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader" scope="col">TD%</th>
column15: <th aria-label="Passes Intercepted" class="poptip center" data-stat="pass_int" data-tip="Interceptions thrown" scope="col">Int</th>
column16: <th aria-label="Pass Intercept. %" class="poptip sort_default_asc hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Pass Intercept. %" data-stat="pass_int_perc" data-tip="Percentage of Times Intercepted when Attempting to Pass <br>Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader.<br />" scope="col">Int%</th>
column17: <th aria-label="Pass 1st Downs" class="poptip center" data-stat="pass_first_down" data-tip="First downs passing" scope="col">1D</th>
column18: <th aria-label="Pass Success Rate" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-stat="pass_success" data-tip="Passing Success Rate<br />A successful pass gains at least 40% of yards required on 1st down, 60% of yards required on 2nd down, and 100% on 3rd or 4th down. Denominator is pass attempts + times sacked." scope="col">Succ%</th>
column19: <th aria-label="Long Pass" class="poptip center" data-stat="pass_long" data-tip="Longest Completed Pass Thrown (complete since 1975)" scope="col">Lng</th>
column20: <th aria-label="Yds/Pass Att" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Yds/Pass Att" data-stat="pass_yds_per_att" data-tip="Yards gained per pass attempt <br>Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.<br>Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." scope="col">Y/A</th>
column21: <th aria-label="Adj Yds/Pass Att" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Adj Yds/Pass Att" data-stat="pass_adj_yds_per_att" data-tip="Adjusted Yards gained per pass attempt<br />(Passing Yards + 20 * Passing TD - 45 * Interceptions) / (Passes Attempted)<br />Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." scope="col">AY/A</th>
column22: <th aria-label="Yds/Pass Cmp" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Yds/Pass Cmp" data-stat="pass_yds_per_cmp" data-tip="<b>Yards gained per pass completion</b> (Passing Yards) / (Passes Completed)<br />Minimum 14 pass attempts per schedule game to qualify as leader.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader" scope="col">Y/C</th>
column23: <th aria-label="Passing Yds/Game" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Passing Yds/Game" data-stat="pass_yds_per_g" data-tip="<b>Yards gained per game played</b><br>Minimum half a game played per scheduled game to qualify as leader.<br>Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader" scope="col">Y/G</th>
column24: <th aria-label="Passer Rating" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Passer Rating" data-stat="pass_rating" data-tip="Passer Rating, <a href='https://www.pro-football-reference.com/about/glossary.htm'>see glossary</a> for details<br>Different ratings are used by the NFL and NCAA.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader, minimum 150 pass attempts for playoffs leader." scope="col">Rate</th>
column25: <th aria-label="QBR" class="poptip show_partial_when_sorting hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="QBR" data-stat="qbr" data-tip="<b>QBR</b><br />ESPN s Total Quarterback Rating, calculated since 2006" scope="col">QBR</th>
column26: <th aria-label="Sacked " class="poptip center" data-stat="pass_sacked" data-tip="Times Sacked (official since 1969, complete NFL coverage since 1963, partial NFL coverage from 1960-62)" scope="col">Sk</th>
column27: <th aria-label="Sacked Yds Lost" class="poptip center" data-stat="pass_sacked_yds" data-tip="Yards lost due to sacks (official since 1969, complete NFL coverage since 1947)" scope="col">Yds</th>
column28: <th aria-label="Sack %" class="poptip sort_default_asc hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Sack %" data-stat="pass_sacked_perc" data-tip="Percentage of Time Sacked when Attempting to Pass: Times Sacked / (Passes Attempted + Times Sacked)<br>Minimum 14 attempts + sacks per scheduled game to qualify as leader.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader" scope="col">Sk%</th>
column29: <th aria-label="Net Yds/Pass Att" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Net Yds/Pass Att" data-stat="pass_net_yds_per_att" data-tip="Net Yards gained per pass attempt<br />(Passing Yards - Sack Yards) / (Passes Attempted + Times Sacked)<br />Minimum 14 attempts per schedule game to qualify as leader.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." scope="col">NY/A</th>
column30: <th aria-label="Adj Net Yds/Pass Att" class="poptip hide_non_quals center" data-filter="1" data-name="Adj Net Yds/Pass Att" data-stat="pass_adj_net_yds_per_att" data-tip="<b>Adjusted Net Yards per Pass Attempt</b><br>(Passing Yards - Sack Yards + (20 * Passing TD) - (45 * Interceptions)) / (Passes Attempted + Times Sacked)<br>Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.<br />Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." scope="col">ANY/A</th>
column31: <th aria-label="Comebacks" class="poptip center" data-stat="comebacks" data-tip="Comebacks led by quarterback.<br />Must be an offensive scoring drive in the 4th quarter, with the team trailing by one score, though not necessarily a drive to take the lead. Only games ending in a win or tie are included." scope="col">4QC</th>
column32: <th aria-label="Game-Winning Drives" class="poptip center" data-stat="gwd" data-tip="Game-winning drives led by quarterback.<br />Must be an offensive scoring drive in the 4th quarter or overtime that puts the winning team ahead for the last time." scope="col">GWD</th>
